Welcome & opening hours

   Located right in downtown Montpellier on the Place de la Comédie, the
   Montpellier Tourist Office is open 7 days a week. Our entire team is at
   your disposal to offer advice and help you organize your stay.
     __________________________________________________________________

Montpellier Comédie

   Committed to Quality processes since 2000, we are proud of our Tourist
   Office's four-star classification and its AFNOR NF certification for
   tourism-related services and of our certification for the Sud de France
   quality label.

   Montpellier Tourist Office staff members welcome you with a smile and
   help you to organize your trip. We are able to provide you with
   personalised recommendations for your stay in many foreign languages :
     * English
     * Spanish
     * German
     * Italian
     * Dutch
     * Japanese

   Every person is dedicated to providing you with service that meets your
   expectations. Please don't hesitate to share your comments with us,
   positive or negative, regarding our service as well as that of our
   partner providers.

   OPENING HOURS

   October to June
   9:30 am - 6:00 pm Monday - Saturday / Thursday: 10 am - 6 pm
   10:00 am - 5:00 pm Sunday and bank holidays all year

   July, August, September
   9:30 am - 7:30 pm Monday - Friday
   10:00 am - 5:00 pm Sunday and bank holidays all year

   Office de Tourisme de Montpellier

   Tél. : +33 (0)4 67 60 60 60
   Fax. : +33 (0)4 67 60 60 61
   Place de la Comédie / Esplanade Charles de Gaulle
   30, allée Jean de Lattre de Tassigny
   34 000 Montpellier

   Access to the Tourist Office :
       By Car : paid parking - Comédie
       By Tramway : Tramway line 1 - Place de la Comédie

   View the map

