Our garden waits for you !

   Our garden behind our welcoming desk is opened !

   Come to check our brochures or to ask for informations on the
   destination.

   New in 2019: the water fountain to refresh you.
     * Opening time:

   Daily 9.30AM - 7.30PM (Mondays to Saturdays)

   10AM - 5PM (Sundays and Bank Holidays)

   Jardin d'accueil de l'Office de Tourisme © OTC3M Jardin d'accueil de
   l'Office de Tourisme

