Tourist Office in Lattes :

   Espace Lattara, Avenue de Montpellier
   34970 Lattes
   Tél : + 33 (0)7 72 43 65 08

   Opening hours:

   From May to September: Open from Tuesday to Friday : 9:30  –
   12:30 and  14:00 – 18:00 & On Saturday :9:30 - 12:30 / 14:00 -17:00
   From october to April: Open from Tuesday to Friday : 9:30  –
   12:30 (until 1pm on Wednesdays) and  13:30 – 17:30  & On Saturday :9:30
   - 13:00

   ►Closed on bank holidays. Closed on August 15th and 16th 2019.

   GPS coordinates : Latitude : 43,567693 ; Longitude : 3,902214
   Maill : contactlattes@ot-montpellier.fr
   More info about Lattes

   Access
   Exit 30 (A9)
   Free Parking de la Poste (limited to 2 hours). Disk at your disposal at
   the Lattes Tourist Office.
   Tramway : Line 3. Change in Boirargues. Stop Lattes Centre (Tourist
   Office at 200m)

Tourist Office in Castries :

   25 rue Sainte-Catherine
   34160 Castries
   Tél : + 33 (0)4 67 52 04 24

   Closed out of summer

   OPEN IN SUMMERTIME from July 1st to August 30th 2019
   monday to friday from 9.30am to 12.30 and 2pm to 5pm

   ►Closed on bank holidays.

   GPS coordinates : Latitude : 43,673489 ; Longitude : 3,982602

   E-Mail : contactcastries@ot-montpellier.fr

   More info about Castries

   Access
   Exit 28 (A709)
   Free Parking for visitors
   Tramway : until Castelnau le lez (P+Tram Notre Dame de Sablassou) then
   bus 112 (Hérault Transport) , [or line 27 ou line 31 (if booked 1 hour
   in advance with TAM)] : Stop Centre (Tourist Office at 200 meters)

   No access for disabled persons

Tourist Office in Villeneuve-les-Maguelone :

   Centre culturel Bérenger de Fréjol

   235 boulevard des Moures 34750 Villeneuve les Maguelone

   Closed out of summer season

   OPEN IN SUMMERTIME
   In June open on the week-ends : 15th & 16th of June, 22nd & 23rd of
   June, 29th & 30th of June.

   from July 2nd to August 31st 2019
   from tuesday to saturday 9.30am to 12.30 and from 2pm to 5pm

   ►Closed on bank holidays.

   Mail : contactvlm@ot-montpellier.fr

   GPS coordinates : Latitude : 43,528685 ; Longitude : 3,862059 View map

