Would you rather?

   Would you rather stay in Montpellier with friends, family, as a couple
   or with best deal stay?
     __________________________________________________________________

   Family

   Montpellier is the ideal family destination: suggestions for outings
   with the kids, family holiday  offers, wide range of activities for
   adults and children.
   Equitation Montpellier © Equitation Montpellier - C.Ramat-Leclant
   Good deals

   Find great deals that will make your stay in Montpellier even more
   unforgettable.
   Bon plan gratuit © Bon plan gratuit - OT Montpellier
   Couple

   Romantic side of Montpellier: ideas for romantic holidays, Valentine's
   Day or a romantic dinner for two in Montpellier.
   Best romantic european destination © Best romantic european destination
   Montpellier Tourisme
   With friends

   Montpellier with friends: shopping, restaurants, thrilling activities,
   places to go out and more.
   En tribu à Montpellier © KFH
   Language schools

   Montpellier, an international city and student town, successfully
   organises language-learning trips with its many language schools to
   help students learn French.
   Faculté de droit de Montpellier © Les Editions Chabot du Lez

